{"tid":1788973,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"後生女黃凱儀(波波)胸大勁煩惱","createTime":"2019-12-19T06:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T14:00:12.000Z","uid":153318,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"37bebe1fb71fe9bab3e0a56d36ab90f0bf0d5784","tid":1788973,"uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:17:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191219/bkn-20191219100014010-1219_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20191219%2Fbkn-20191219100014010-1219_00862_001.html&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6mLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=e92170d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191219/bkn-20191219100014010-1219_00862_001.html</a><br />\n「後生女」黃凱儀（波波）憑無綫J2台節目《#後生仔傾吓偈》而為人認識，性格開朗的她，視「食玩瞓」為人生最大樂事。黃凱儀英文名叫Krysella，但暱稱「波波」明顯更受歡迎，她解釋「波波」的由來：「幾年前開始拍片上網，可能Krysella讀起嚟累贅同難記，所以條片上網後，留言出現咗『波波』呢個名，開頭諗唔係叫我呀嘛？網民話個名襯我，咁其實我都知咩事，佢哋要咁嗌，我都接受。（唔介意？）都覺得好記，我係玩得嘅人，冇所謂。（事實你真係有料？）係特徵嚟，冇法，係媽咪遺傳，我姨媽身材最勁！真心就算我依家瘦咗都冇影響，所以某程度都係萬幸嘅。」 <br />\n<br />\n 最鍾意食雞翼<br />\n不過，波波不會將身材看得太重，更曾經為之煩惱：「我懷疑食得激素多，比平常人早少少發育，早到阿媽要帶我去睇醫生，睇吓係咪正常！」為何覺得與激素有關？她笑言可能與瘋狂愛吃雞翼有關，由細到大雞翼都是她的最愛，之前到名古屋拍節目，連掃超過30間雞翼店：「去試邊間最好食，一日食三十幾隻，好誇張，但我都唔厭！」<br />\n比唔起麥明詩馮盈盈<br />\n忙於幕前工作的她，去年決心繼續學業，修讀商科副學士學位，她承認受《後》三位主持麥明詩、馮盈盈與陸浩明影響：「佢哋讀書叻、轉數快，我唔係擦鞋，係認真，發現同佢哋講嘢，自己入面乜都冇，就算唔同三個比，只係同班『後生仔』比，都覺得自己究竟做緊啲乜！佢哋好有目標，知道要乜，我淨係食玩瞓，兩年就咁虛度光陰，所以決心再讀書，搵自己想做嘅嘢做好佢。」"},{"pid":"e9c26fe40e5f605a36d93e32cdb8baf12e15c1ee","tid":1788973,"uid":13118,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:17:58.000Z","msg":"伯母我黎喇"},{"pid":"136f6ec4823ce1dd6c3d71f3f7e27b89fdfc7bc6","tid":1788973,"uid":76098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:18:42.000Z","msg":"叫呀儀既通常都大波"},{"pid":"a36c4b336a7e193f04f7a4a446cbff14a944a32f","tid":1788973,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:19:05.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"937867728d34516ccfdb5299bc55aeb02fed5a7c","tid":1788973,"uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:19:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/krysellawong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fkrysellawong%2F&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6mLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=635d8c69\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/krysellawong/</a><br />\n樣貌唔算突出，不過tvb奀星都應該砌得"},{"pid":"77e2c9c41f9c2b82877efade9f86ac0015637cd7","tid":1788973,"uid":5944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"136f6ec4823ce1dd6c3d71f3f7e27b89fdfc7bc6","tid":1788973,"uid":76098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:18:42.000Z","msg":"叫呀儀既通常都大波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:20:09.000Z","msg":"但我第一個係諗起嘅阿儀係小儀"},{"pid":"d3f565216f1f0577267b9fa12184dab0b3d5267a","tid":1788973,"uid":28858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:20:56.000Z","msg":"波大遮三醜"},{"pid":"3fb408dae29af7b9fc1484eb71af15de2c5f4cd1","tid":1788973,"uid":222907,"like":9,"dislike":10,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"136f6ec4823ce1dd6c3d71f3f7e27b89fdfc7bc6","tid":1788973,"uid":76098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:18:42.000Z","msg":"叫呀儀既通常都大波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:20:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r5WOr3g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr5WOr3g.jpg&h=7694c3b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"890268907de80618dbbe70a5e3ff9911beda0aee","tid":1788973,"uid":4179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:21:08.000Z","msg":"呢條女我有fd係club ons過"},{"pid":"7b336f1b3bdf7ffc89795bb359838ccfc483fa7f","tid":1788973,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"890268907de80618dbbe70a5e3ff9911beda